 in a way that preserves the principle of covariance\nof General Relativity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Feb 2015 02:26:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 26 Mar 2015 10:54:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-07-08"}
