pe\nI factors, with one summand for each irreducible representation of $A$. The\nself-adjoint part of any unital separable C*-algebra is isomorphic to the\nBanach space of strongly affine real-valued functions on its state space.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Feb 2015 12:23:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 9 Jun 2015 10:14:44 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 19 Jul 2016 00:27:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-07-20"}
